583
00:25:03,680 --> 00:25:04,760
Of course

584
00:25:05,400 --> 00:25:07,060
it was immensely satisfying.

585
00:25:07,880 --> 00:25:09,040
Exactly!

586
00:25:09,160 --> 00:25:10,040
Prince of Dingbei came

587
00:25:10,040 --> 00:25:11,760
