588
00:25:12,300 --> 00:25:15,660
So maybe, the legitimate daughter of the Marquis of Jing'an

589
00:25:15,690 --> 00:25:18,290
and our kingdom's war god, Prince of Dingbei,

590
00:25:18,680 --> 00:25:20,610
