632
00:27:08,680 --> 00:27:09,400
You may go.

633
00:27:09,760 --> 00:27:10,690
Yes, Your Grace.

634
00:27:15,690 --> 00:27:16,850
If the Ming family

635
00:27:17,290 --> 00:27:19,200
