00:29:36,560 --> 00:29:38,680
You were painted so vividly.

681
00:29:39,240 --> 00:29:40,080
Besides,

682
00:29:40,080 --> 00:29:42,500
you're like a shining pearl,

683
00:29:42,600 --> 00:29:44,040
even with a veil,

684
00:29:44,080 --> 00:29:45,680
your charm is unmistakable.

685
00:29:46,160 --> 00:29:47,820
How could I not recognize you?

686
00:29:49,200 --> 00:29:50,160
Suxin must be worried,

687
00:29:50,160 --> 00:29:51,490
