711
00:30:51,280 --> 00:30:53,540
What, have they all been eating for free?

712
00:30:53,760 --> 00:30:55,840
Zhang Ji is Duke of Ling's trusted man,

713
00:30:55,840 --> 00:30:57,240
not someone to take lightly.

714
00:30:57,240 --> 00:30:59,100
With so many people here tonight,

715
00:30:59,280 --> 00:31:01,280
it's no easy task to arrest someone.

716
00:31:02,440 --> 00:31:04,100
Save the wine for another day.

717
00:31:05,600 --> 00:31:06,990
What's going on?

718
00:31:14,400 --> 00:31:16,350
-Tan.
-Minmin.

719
00:31:26,120 --> 00:31:27,680
Tan, I'm here to save you!

720
00:31:27,680 --> 00:31:28,680
-Someone help!
- Someone help!

721
00:31:28,680 --> 00:31:29,240
I won't let you go!

722
00:31:29,240 --> 00:31:30,440
Do you want her to die?

723
00:31:38,900 --> 00:31:39,680
Make way!

724
00:31:39,680 --> 00:31:40,600
Move aside! Move aside!

725
00:31:40,600 --> 00:31:41,540
Miss Minmin!

726
00:31:41,680 --> 00:31:43,680
Suxin, thank goodness you're here.

