731
00:31:47,880 --> 00:31:49,200
He must not approach Tan.

732
00:31:49,200 --> 00:31:50,110
And send more people

733
00:31:50,110 --> 00:31:51,350
to keep the crowd back.

734
00:31:51,350 --> 00:31:52,280
No one must find out

735
00:31:52,280 --> 00:31:52,960
that it was Tan who fell in.

736
00:31:52,960 --> 00:31:53,690
Understood.

737
00:32:10,240 --> 00:32:11,490
Who are you?

738
00:32:15,080 --> 00:32:16,160
Take him away.

739
00:32:16,640 --> 00:32:17,840
Interrogate him thoroughly.

740
00:32:17,840 --> 00:32:18,280
Yes, sir.

741
00:32:18,280 --> 00:32:19,120
Let go of me!

742
00:32:20,680 --> 00:32:21,640
Let go!

743
00:32:22,760 --> 00:32:23,720
Help!

744
00:32:24,880 --> 00:32:25,990
Help!

745
00:32:43,480 --> 00:32:44,440
You again?

746
00:32:50,360 --> 00:32:52,040
If this girl really is from a noble family,

747
00:32:52,040 --> 00:32:54,080
