748
00:32:54,080 --> 00:32:55,610
No outsiders allowed near.

749
00:32:56,840 --> 00:32:59,160
Miss Minmin, what should we do now?

750
00:32:59,560 --> 00:33:00,590
Tan,

751
00:33:00,840 --> 00:33:02,360
