769
00:33:48,440 --> 00:33:49,080
Found out

770
00:33:49,080 --> 00:33:50,560
it was the Duke of Chang's daughter.

771
00:33:50,560 --> 00:33:51,240
She was in a hurry to save her.

772
00:33:51,240 --> 00:33:51,840
Thought maybe

773
00:33:51,840 --> 00:33:53,680
it was the Ming family's daughter who fell in.

774
00:33:53,680 --> 00:33:55,280
Oh, and Liang Zixuan was there too.

775
00:33:55,280 --> 00:33:56,480
He didn't listen to anyone,

776
00:33:56,480 --> 00:33:57,940
just jumped in to save her.

777
00:33:58,560 --> 00:33:59,480
Seeing how determined he was,

778
00:33:59,480 --> 00:34:00,960
those who knew said it was urgent.

779
00:34:00,960 --> 00:34:01,560
But to outsiders,

780
00:34:01,560 --> 00:34:03,080
it may seem premeditated.

781
00:34:03,100 --> 00:34:05,000
A woman soaked

782
00:34:05,020 --> 00:34:06,880
and carried out by a man in front of a crowd,

783
00:34:06,880 --> 00:34:08,639
what's left of her reputation?

784
00:34:10,100 --> 00:34:11,620
You think Liang Zixuan

785
00:34:11,679 --> 00:34:13,280
