786
00:34:13,340 --> 00:34:14,850
The Ming and Liang families have long had a betrothal.

787
00:34:14,850 --> 00:34:15,730
This move

788
00:34:15,840 --> 00:34:17,679
forces the Ming family's hand.

789
00:34:20,880 --> 00:34:23,679
