790
00:34:24,199 --> 00:34:25,520
But they'll never

791
00:34:27,000 --> 00:34:28,400
get this marriage.

792
00:34:29,800 --> 00:34:31,679
Send this hairpin to the Ming household.

793
00:34:31,679 --> 00:34:32,679
Say their young lady

794
00:34:32,679 --> 00:34:34,000
has already returned home.

795
00:34:34,000 --> 00:34:35,360
Have someone go to the docks

796
00:34:35,360 --> 00:34:36,690
and smooth things over.

797
00:34:42,080 --> 00:34:43,420
Miss Minmin!

798
00:34:43,840 --> 00:34:44,989
Miss Minmin!

799
00:34:45,480 --> 00:34:46,570
Miss Minmin!

800
00:34:47,040 --> 00:34:47,929
Lyu'e?

801
00:34:47,960 --> 00:34:48,760
Miss Minmin.

802
00:34:49,360 --> 00:34:50,260
Miss Minmin.

803
00:34:50,480 --> 00:34:51,880
Why are you still here?

804
00:34:51,880 --> 00:34:54,000
My lady made glutinous rice balls herself

805
00:34:54,000 --> 00:34:56,659
