806
00:34:59,040 --> 00:35:00,000
What did she say?

807
00:35:00,020 --> 00:35:02,160
My Lady has grown weary from waiting at home.

808
00:35:02,160 --> 00:35:04,060
We'd best hurry back.

809
00:35:08,330 --> 00:35:10,680
It was the heir of Duke of Ling's Mansion

810
00:35:10,680 --> 00:35:12,010
who fell into the water.

811
00:35:12,080 --> 00:35:13,480
Young Master, slow down.

812
00:35:13,760 --> 00:35:14,830
Young Master.

813
00:35:15,480 --> 00:35:16,350
Yes,

814
00:35:16,480 --> 00:35:18,080
Young Master Liang fell into the water.

815
00:35:18,080 --> 00:35:19,680
I happened to pass by

816
00:35:19,680 --> 00:35:20,680
and saw it myself.

817
00:35:20,680 --> 00:35:22,610
I'm sending people to save him now.

818
00:35:29,710 --> 00:35:30,670
Silence.

819
00:35:37,510 --> 00:35:49,270
[Bieyu Mansion]

820
00:35:39,870 --> 00:35:40,780
This is the place.

821
00:35:40,780 --> 00:35:41,500
Let's go.

