00:35:47,100 --> 00:35:47,900
Mr. Wang,

823
00:35:57,050 --> 00:35:58,580
Miss Ming, you've woken up.

824
00:36:00,030 --> 00:36:00,830
You...

825
00:36:01,130 --> 00:36:02,330
Who are you?

826
00:36:02,410 --> 00:36:03,970
No need to worry, Miss Ming.

827
00:36:03,990 --> 00:36:05,630
I am Zhang Huaiyu.

828
00:36:06,640 --> 00:36:07,680
You saved me?

829
00:36:07,680 --> 00:36:09,320
