830
00:36:09,800 --> 00:36:10,480
Here.

831
00:36:12,680 --> 00:36:14,400
He's the one who saved you.

832
00:36:18,240 --> 00:36:19,390
You again?

833
00:36:19,560 --> 00:36:20,120
Again?

834
00:36:20,440 --> 00:36:21,540
You two know each other?

835
00:36:21,540 --> 00:36:22,740
-We do not.
-We do not.

836
00:36:29,000 --> 00:36:29,840
Miss Ming,

837
00:36:30,000 --> 00:36:31,680
you were in danger of drowning just now.

838
00:36:31,680 --> 00:36:32,640
Had it not been for

839
00:36:32,640 --> 00:36:33,540
Xu's quick rescue,

840
00:36:33,540 --> 00:36:34,460
you might

841
00:36:35,120 --> 00:36:36,900
not have kept your reputation.

842
00:36:42,440 --> 00:36:43,440
Then I thank you.

843
00:36:44,780 --> 00:36:45,580
Miss Ming.

