856
00:37:08,440 --> 00:37:09,800
We are even now,

857
00:37:10,440 --> 00:37:12,040
and need not meet again.

858
00:37:12,400 --> 00:37:13,880
Next time you fall into water,

859
00:37:13,880 --> 00:37:15,610
