895
00:38:47,760 --> 00:38:48,760
The Liang family?

896
00:39:03,200 --> 00:39:05,440
Good, good, good.

897
00:39:05,600 --> 00:39:07,330
How could Tan be in such a place?

898
00:39:07,400 --> 00:39:08,860
You must have heard wrong.

899
00:39:09,480 --> 00:39:11,080
