910
00:39:32,280 --> 00:39:32,760
Well...

911
00:39:33,560 --> 00:39:35,200
Young lady. Who are you looking for?

912
00:39:35,200 --> 00:39:36,160
I can help.

913
00:39:36,160 --> 00:39:36,960
No need.

914
00:39:37,280 --> 00:39:38,840
Young lady, I...

