919
00:39:44,080 --> 00:39:44,760
Pretentious.

920
00:39:44,760 --> 00:39:45,480
Young lady.

921
00:39:45,480 --> 00:39:46,200
Move.

922
00:39:47,680 --> 00:39:48,680
Stop right there.

923
00:39:52,520 --> 00:39:53,320
You...

