927
00:40:00,680 --> 00:40:02,280
Aren't you looking for someone?

928
00:40:02,280 --> 00:40:03,310
I know.

929
00:40:03,880 --> 00:40:05,320
If you want to find her,

930
00:40:05,360 --> 00:40:06,880
apologize to me first.

931
00:40:11,080 --> 00:40:12,080
Apologize?

932
00:40:14,720 --> 00:40:15,480
No apology,

933
00:40:15,480 --> 00:40:16,520
but a fist ready.

934
00:40:19,440 --> 00:40:20,240
Lead the way.

935
00:40:21,840 --> 00:40:22,480
I...

936
00:40:26,240 --> 00:40:27,040
Tan!

937
00:40:28,440 --> 00:40:29,240
Tan!

938
00:40:31,200 --> 00:40:32,000
Where is she?

939
00:40:37,360 --> 00:40:39,600
Strange, she was just here...

940
00:40:41,430 --> 00:40:42,140
She...

941
00:40:42,640 --> 00:40:44,240
She...

942
00:40:45,640 --> 00:40:47,280
Where...

943
00:40:47,280 --> 00:40:48,210
Where did she go?

944
00:40:48,280 --> 00:40:50,280
Sir, according to Zhang Ji's confession,

945
00:40:50,280 --> 00:40:51,760
the Duke of Ling's corruption

946
00:40:51,760 --> 00:40:53,560
