00:40:53,170 --> 00:40:56,450
[Jinyun Guard, Zhuiying]

948
00:40:53,560 --> 00:40:55,240
But the Duchess of Ling

949
00:40:55,240 --> 00:40:56,080
has already sent Zhu'er

950
00:40:56,080 --> 00:40:57,280
out of the capital overnight.

951
00:40:57,280 --> 00:40:58,480
She's heading south.

952
00:41:09,160 --> 00:41:09,960
Hold on.

953
00:41:10,360 --> 00:41:11,680
Why are you investigating Zhu'er?

954
00:41:11,680 --> 00:41:13,200
Why dig into the Duke of Ling's Mansion's affairs?

955
00:41:13,200 --> 00:41:14,400
Who are you,

956
00:41:14,440 --> 00:41:16,100
and what are your intentions?

957
00:41:17,480 --> 00:41:19,880
If you want to live, don't meddle.

958
00:41:20,530 --> 00:41:22,190
Don't ask what you shouldn't.

959
00:41:22,360 --> 00:41:24,620
Don't get involved where you shouldn't.

960
00:41:24,880 --> 00:41:25,960
If I really stayed out

961
00:41:25,960 --> 00:41:27,240
of the Liang family's business,

962
00:41:27,240 --> 00:41:28,600
I wouldn't live long.

963
00:41:29,160 --> 00:41:30,680
My fiancé, Liang Zixuan,

964
00:41:31,040 --> 00:41:32,660
has been having a secret affair with Zhu'er,

965
00:41:32,660 --> 00:41:34,080
and she's pregnant.

966
00:41:34,280 --> 00:41:35,640
Once she leaves the capital,

967
00:41:35,640 --> 00:41:37,120
there will be no proof,

968
00:41:37,200 --> 00:41:39,800
and I won't be able to break off the engagement.

969
00:41:41,480 --> 00:41:43,170
I... I can see

970
00:41:44,640 --> 00:41:45,760
you don't seem like a

971
00:41:45,760 --> 00:41:47,120
cold-blooded villain.

972
00:41:47,540 --> 00:41:49,640
Otherwise, you wouldn't have saved me earlier.

973
00:41:49,640 --> 00:41:50,880
I don't care why you're

974
00:41:50,880 --> 00:41:52,160
investigating the Duke of Ling,

975
00:41:52,160 --> 00:41:54,090
but the enemy of my enemy is my ally.

976
00:41:54,480 --> 00:41:56,360
We're more or less

977
00:41:56,360 --> 00:41:57,600
in the same boat.

978
00:42:00,680 --> 00:42:02,040
You wouldn't really

979
00:42:02,450 --> 00:42:04,380
stand by and let an innocent like me

980
00:42:05,280 --> 00:42:06,800
suffer lifelong misery

981
00:42:07,800 --> 00:42:10,000
because of the Liang family, would you?

982
00:42:15,880 --> 00:42:17,410
You care about reputation,

983
00:42:17,640 --> 00:42:18,970
