00:43:47,800 --> 00:43:50,010
to a steward

1023
00:43:50,080 --> 00:43:51,920
on a country estate in Lizhou.

1024
00:43:52,540 --> 00:43:55,000
She won't show her face in the capital again.

1025
00:43:56,560 --> 00:43:57,680
And how can you guarantee

1026
00:43:57,680 --> 00:43:59,400
