1027
00:43:59,880 --> 00:44:01,240
and cause trouble?

1028
00:44:01,240 --> 00:44:01,920
I...

1029
00:44:03,680 --> 00:44:04,480
I...

1030
00:44:06,880 --> 00:44:08,280
Make her disappear.
